# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Unsealed — .gitignore
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Keep out of the public repo:
#   1. Anything that could leak server credentials, IPs, or the
#      operator's dev environment
#   2. Submitted case data (zero-knowledge guarantee — must never
#      leave the server)
#   3. Local build artifacts, OS cruft, editor swap files
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── CREDENTIALS & SECRETS ────────────────────────────────────
# NEVER commit these. They live on the server only.
api_keys.env
config.php
*.env
*.env.local
.env*
!.env.example
*.key
*.pem
*.pfx
*.p12
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
id_ecdsa*
*authorized_keys*
known_hosts
ssh_config

# ─── SUBMISSION DATA ──────────────────────────────────────────
# The submissions database is the single source of truth for user
# cases. Zero-knowledge guarantee means it must never be committed.
data/
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
order_hashes.tsv
press_inquiries*
profile_queue.json

# ─── CLAUDE CODE / AI ASSISTANT LOCAL CONFIG ──────────────────
# Contains approval patterns that may include command examples
# with credentials embedded.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/user_context.json
.claude/**/*.sqlite
.claude/logs/

# ─── LOCAL DEV HELPERS ────────────────────────────────────────
# Any file starting with underscore is a local dev helper — merge
# scripts, deploy tools, audit scripts, one-shot migrations. Not
# useful to external contributors and often contain IP addresses,
# batch-specific data, or server paths.
_*
# Pyc cache
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# ─── DEPLOY ARTIFACTS ─────────────────────────────────────────
# The server-side canonical file is index.html (mirror of the main
# HTML). Keep the authoritative copy (family_court_full_platform_v2.html)
# and let the deploy script regenerate the mirror.
index.html

# ─── EDITOR / OS CRUFT ────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.bak
*.orig
*.tmp
.history/

# ─── NODE / BUILD (if any contributor adds build tooling later) ─
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.cache/
coverage/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log

# ─── BACKUPS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.backup
*.old
*-backup
backup/

# ─── LIVE DATA DUMPS ──────────────────────────────────────────
# These are downloaded snapshots of live data. Can be regenerated;
# don't commit to avoid stale data in repo.
live_*.html.cache
*.live.json

# ─── TEMP ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
/tmp/
tmp/
scratch/

# ─── RAW SOURCE WORKBOOKS ────────────────────────────────────
# The ACF Excel workbooks are huge (30MB+) and already ingested
# into acf_state_data.json. Contributors work from the JSON, not
# the raw Excel. Keep the originals out of the repo.
ACF Excel/
*.xlsx
*.xls
*.xlsm

# ─── ORPHANED VULNERABLE PAGES (deleted from server) ─────────
# These files called api.anthropic.com directly from the browser,
# leaking user IP + case details. Server copies are purged. Local
# copies are kept out of git so they don't accidentally get
# redeployed or picked up by contributors.
ai_complaint_module.html
document_scanner.html
rep_letter_ratings.html
template_detector.html
live_data_integration.html
live_data_layer.html
prosedadai_integration.html
earnings_state_module.html
revenue_scanner_financial.html
legislative_module.html
judge_module.html
attorney_module.html
court_professional_directory.html
court_map.html
family_court_full_platform.html
submit_form_enhance.js

# ─── MISC DEV NOTES ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Internal planning + setup docs that reference server paths,
# credentials, or operator workflow. Replaced by CONTRIBUTING.md
# and SECURITY.md for public contributors.
anonymous_key_guide.md
API_KEYS_SETUP.md
deployment_guide.md
data_integrity_audit.md
attorney_intake_process.md
ingestion_*.md
operator_*.md

# ─── BACKUP ARCHIVES ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Old versioned zips created during development. Snapshot cruft
# — never belongs in a code repo.
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.rar
*.7z

# ─── ENHANCEMENT / INTAKE SCRATCH ─────────────────────────────
# Files that were workbench-style iterations, now either merged
# into the main app or superseded. Not part of the public code.
enhanced_campaign_finance.js
court_directory.json
attorney_intake_*.json
